                  <desc type="foundation">According to the local tradition, the founder was "šǝm Bagunāy" (a governor of Bugnā?); in the time of King Fāsiladas (r. 1632-67). 
                     But according to Additio 5 of BMQM-006, the church was founded during the 6th year of the reign of King ʾIyoʾās (=1761 A.D.)</desc>
